{"tid":2388433,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解拒絕人不能狠心一點？ 呢個係咩心態？","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T11:24:55.000Z","uid":382363,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"89296e76c98b183b4abaf96da9a887ad5d6830b4","tid":2388433,"uid":382363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"(朋友無連登ac 借我ac想上黎問各位意見 利申：男）<br />\n對方一早都同你講無可能<br />\n但心裡又知你中意佢<br />\n唔介意一直同你做朋友好熱情咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係咩心態？<br />\n其實係香港地真係有超多呢類人<br />\n我真係唔明 如果係我果斷講再見就算<br />\n我以前都有預過呢個case 我覺得放棄就算<br />\n<br />\n真正的好女仔會直接拒絕<br />\n唔會留有一絲的機會仲同你傾計<br />\n咁樣我覺得同吊住你無分別<br />\n<br />\n（純個人意見）"},{"pid":"718d8a2d48434a56d76de701cc87c47244dabd83","tid":2388433,"uid":379493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"仲有一大堆人騎牛搵馬<br />\n一路同你發展不錯<br />\n一路積極地去識其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f13926b1c2a7159ea6cf2059a5e99f4f6d1cb1b","tid":2388433,"uid":252789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"原來你坐後備座"},{"pid":"380bf1270619c8ac2a170b5eecd3707726a0ac28","tid":2388433,"uid":23495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"俾人鐘意 有人對你好 係人都開心<br />\n所以唔係個個都咁好人肯同你講<br />\n而且佢有無叫你對佢好"},{"pid":"a27fcf443be47b3f0921e6a41080acdac25d9c9b","tid":2388433,"uid":17932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"係，同樣情況<br />\n玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91e22558d16b2eb21652281a755630ab2b39e2e","tid":2388433,"uid":217555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"港女最中意戴住貞節牌坊收兵<br />\n又要名聲又要著數<br />\n港女咁自我 邊會唔用哂身邊資源"}]}